org.apache.flink.contrib.operatorstatistics

类 OperatorStatisticsConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.contrib.operatorstatistics.OperatorStatisticsConfig
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable

    public class OperatorStatisticsConfig
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Configures the behavior of an OperatorStatistics instance. Sets the parameters that determine the accuracy of the count distinct and heavy hitter sketches Defines the statistics to be collected. A boolean field indicates whether a given statistic should be collected or not Encapsulates an enum indicating which sketch should be used for count distinct and another indicating which sketch should be used for detecting heavy hitters.
